{"tid":1971568,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「半澤直樹2」驚見台灣國旗：防盜版神器","createTime":"2020-04-14T04:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T02:39:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8c17e71fc14007852e8f9aa16c5b0f4a70e751d9","tid":1971568,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IC.RTTGcaCFGKIr_T3gzMg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/b20da7ebcc886452b7a82a7fc499e45d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIC.RTTGcaCFGKIr_T3gzMg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2Fb20da7ebcc886452b7a82a7fc499e45d&h=2c90635d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／翻攝自TBS公式 YouTuboo YouTube<br />\n<br />\n春季檔期的日、韓劇即將陸續開播，韓星李敏鎬退伍後的第一部作品就是和《鬼怪》的編劇金銀淑合作，而日劇《半澤直樹》第二季預告片也曝光了，畫面裡竟然出現台灣國旗，讓影迷又驚又喜，也讓網友忍不住開玩笑討論，該不會是為了防大陸盜版，才刻意安排這個畫面。<br />\n<br />\n半澤直樹坐在辦公桌忙著講電話，但背後的全球23個股市的漲跌幅，畫面正中間出現了台灣兩個字，並且放上國旗。旁邊還有五星旗以及香港區旗，被眼尖網友截圖放到網路討論，笑說「可能是日本電視台的防盜版機制」，也好奇「大陸會不會要求下架」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%8A%E6%BE%A4%E7%9B%B4%E6%A8%B92-%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%8B%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97-%E7%B6%B2%E7%AC%91-%E9%98%B2%E7%9B%9C%E7%89%88%E7%A5%9E%E5%99%A8-032004092.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258D%258A%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%25A8%25B92-%25E9%25A9%259A%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2597-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25AC%2591-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%259B%259C%25E7%2589%2588%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%2599%25A8-032004092.html&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B83wORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=4b1647f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%8A%E6%BE%A4%E7%9B%B4%E6%A8%B92-%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%8B%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97-%E7%B6%B2%E7%AC%91-%E9%98%B2%E7%9B%9C%E7%89